      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t好萊塢左派電影是屎，支麻電影就不是屎了？兩者皆不看才是正常人，變革什麼的就洗洗睡吧。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-07-24",
      "agree_count": 2,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "672988",
      "is_folded": false,
